{"tid":1656143,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［戰略討論］香港人要贏，就只有一條路","createTime":"2019-10-15T12:19:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T15:48:51.000Z","uid":39021,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"24fd0625681ec9e59fbdbd1918f92b98db744e09","tid":1656143,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:19:24.000Z","msg":"中共係本世紀最強大獨裁政權，佢係絕對唔會容許你有民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">連價值不高既新疆都要全面控制，香港咁值錢，中共有咩可能會放手？</span></strong><br />\n即使攬炒戰略成功，香港地位下降，中共只會更肆無忌憚地控制香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港要有民主，就只有一個可能性<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係中國國力大幅衰退</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陳雲不斷講「全黨死清光」，現實係中共不死，香港不生<br />\n而中國國力要大幅衰退，只可能有兩個原因<br />\n1. 中國內外交困，引致經濟內爆，民眾暴動<br />\n2. 共產黨因權鬥失控完全倒台<br />\n<br />\n所以，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港短期內係絕對無可能贏，呢場係長期抗爭</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我地要好清楚自己既戰略目標<br />\n要記住，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地本身就係中共春袋，春袋特點係外露，香港係唯一「外露」既中國城市</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要贏，就要中共收皮，要中共收皮有兩大方向<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>1. 外力<br />\n－令外國意識到中國係全球最大威脅，最終聯合抗共<br />\n－借外國輿論限制中國能夠出既牌（例如出兵）<br />\n2. 內力<br />\n－靠永續抗爭，不斷為中國經濟同政治製造不穩定因素</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n大家決定行動時，要認清每一個行動既終極目標<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>爆鋪</strong></span>可以減低中共對香港既影響力，但爆鋪唔係主動技，實際上只係拖延戰術，不能期望過高<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>私了</strong></span>係為咗保護自己人，確保抗爭能夠永續落去<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>遊行抗爭</strong></span>無可能令到中共直接跪低，但透過慢性向大陸輸出革命之火，長期延續不穩定因素，令中國更易內爆<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>國際戰線</strong></span>可以令到外國統一抗共，呢到都有兩大戰線，第一係道德牌（西藏新疆人權問題），第二係恐懼牌（中共不斷透過資本控制全球，NBA及暴雪事件）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>知道目標後，就要謹慎行事<br />\n每一個行動，都要問清楚自己呢個行動點樣可以協助達到最終目標</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91ffd84bbe2d4fb02dccfef0338947b4da19d04","tid":1656143,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:26:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec6df165f650a9135821c27125a1513c4da55e4","tid":1656143,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d8094cb2f9c08ab016d15e6ef5c0c42898f301","tid":1656143,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d039c49860a98927d27cd7fb21398c3bcff45d","tid":1656143,"uid":333508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:31:52.000Z","msg":"推 認同真正大佬係中共dllm"},{"pid":"f71cc880662127b14135389971d50972df24cea6","tid":1656143,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:34:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48a85e